column5: I hope you all have a great day and weekend, with your families and loved ones!!!!  I hope you all stocked up on ibuprophen and toothbrushes!!!!  HAPPY EASTER!
happy Easter ro all. I have three of my four daughters coming with all of theirs The little guys (5) all under six! Planned to BBq lamb and the light snow flurries is not going to stop me.

Happy Easter from us too. We are hiding out from Easter dinner from the family today. I've always wanted to play hooky from a family dinner, todays the day. Ever feel good and bad at the same time. Off to Port Dover for perch. The freezers empty of fish now.

Happy Easter OFC'ers. I had my 2 brothers, 2 sister-in-laws, 5 of my nieces and nephews, and my mother and step-father over for a wonderful turkey dinner that my wife made. That makes 15 of us!. Was a great day and I am truly blessed and thankful for my family.
